ack\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104iub1665702713124.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/iub1665702713124.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/iub1665702713124.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"iub1665702713124\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">$FULL_SYNTAX\n  </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify the allowed character set for the field syntax definition, when the full character range is specified (<code class=\"ph codeph\">FUL</code> shorthand code).\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"iub1665702713124__topic_d140495e1_d140496e1_d140497e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"iub1665702713124__p_d140498e1_d140499e1_d140500e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$FULL_SYNTAX</span>{<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>} <code class=\"ph codeph\">unicode</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">v8</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">bmp</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">latin-1</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">ascii</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"iub1665702713124__section_ljr_snx_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d99532e82\">Arguments </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"iub1665702713124__ul_dg3_vnx_bwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"iub1665702713124__li_d49670e1_d49671e1_d49672e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">unicode</code>—full range of Unicode\n          character set. This is the default value. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"iub1665702713124__li_d49673e1_d49674e1_d49675e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">v8</code>—full range of Unicode character\n          set plus Uniface meta characters missing in Unicode. For more information, see the\n          \"Unicode Compatibility Issues\" topic. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"iub1665702713124__li_d49676e1_d49677e1_d49678e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">bmp</code>—Unicode BMP characters. For more\n          information, see the \"Unicode\" topic.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"iub1665702713124__li_d49679e1_d49680e1_d49681e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">latin-1</code>—ISO 8859-1 character set for\n          Western European languages. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"iub1665702713124__li_d49682e1_d49683e1_d49684e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">ascii</code>—ASCII characters. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"iub1665702713124__section_l5w_snx_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d99532e116\">Defaults </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"iub1665702713124__table_d16730e1_d16731e1_d16732e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Assignment file: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Client assignment files, usys.asn,\n                  <span class=\"ph filepath\">ide.asn</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Section: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">[SETTINGS] </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">unicode</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jjg1714304600909.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Field Syntax Codes</a><p>Field syntax codes specify the data entry pattern, the allowed characters, and whether fields are mandatory or read-only.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vmy1665702874862.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Unicode Compatibility Issues</a><p>Earlier versions of Uniface used the Uniface meta character set as its internal character set. Uniface 9 uses Unicode as its internal character set. For compatibility reasons, the meta character set is still used, but this results in some problems. Assignment settings are available to solve these issues.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/udi1665702731005.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Unicode</a><p>Unicode is an industry standard designed to allow text and symbols from all languages to be consistently represented and manipulated by computers.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528709\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528709\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$FULL_SYNTAX Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $FULL_SYNTAX Specify the allowed character set for the field syntax definition, when the full character range is specified ( FUL shorthand code). $FULL_SYNTAX { = } unicode | v8 | bmp | latin-1 | ascii Arguments unicode —full range of Unicode character set. This is the default value. v8 —full range of Unicode character set plus Uniface meta characters missing in Unicode. For more information, see the \"Unicode Compatibility Issues\" topic. bmp —Unicode BMP characters. For more information, see the \"Unicode\" topic. latin-1 —ISO 8859-1 character set for Western European languages. ascii —ASCII characters. Defaults Assignment file: Client assignment files, usys.asn, ide.asn Section: [SETTINGS] Default value: unicode Related Links Field Syntax Codes Field syntax codes specify the data entry pattern, the allowed characters, and whether fields are mandatory or read-only. Unicode Compatibility Issues Earlier versions of Uniface used the Uniface meta character set as its internal character set. Uniface 9 uses Unicode as its internal character set. For compatibility reasons, the meta character set is still used, but this results in some problems. Assignment settings are available to solve these issues. Unicode Unicode is an industry standard designed to allow text and symbols from all languages to be consistently represented and manipulated by computers. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}